the 1 st Independence Battalion.

24
00:02:38,124 --> 00:02:42,151
We came to Sonora with the boldest hearts
and the loftiest of intentions.

25
00:02:43,730 --> 00:02:46,062
But I will not dissemble with you.

26
00:02:46,166 --> 00:02:48,464
