Not guilty.

73
00:05:57,590 --> 00:06:00,821
- Not guilty.
- [Whooping, Cheering]

74
00:06:00,927 --> 00:06:02,588
<i>[Man]</i>
<i>Hear.! Hear.! </i>

75
00:06:02,695 --> 00:06:05,357
<i>Hey, where do we go next, Colonel? </i>

76
