<i>Walker.! Walker.! Walker.! Walker.! </i>

122
00:11:11,237 --> 00:11:13,933
<i>[Walker Narrating] In the flurry</i>
<i>of excitement following his acquittal... </i>

123
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:17,771
<i>Walker received an invitation</i>
<i>from that famous captain of industry... </i>

124
00:11:17,877 --> 00:11:20,175
