I'm so pleased to see you.

128
00:11:40,132 --> 00:11:42,464
I can't tell you how happy
this will make the commodore.

129
00:11:42,568 --> 00:11:44,468
Give him some water,
would you, please?

130
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:46,868
Every day he's been asking,
"When will Colonel Walker arrive?"

131
00:11:46,972 --> 00:11:49,566
- Is my horse gonna be safe with that man?
- Yes, he'll be fine.

132
00:11:49,675 --> 00:11:52,235
You have been very much
on his mind.

133
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:55,804
Central America, Colonel.

134
00:11:55,915 --> 00:11:59,112
There's land, and all of it
there for the taking.

135
00:12:01,587 --> 00:12:04,784
Think of it, sir.
From ocean to ocean.

136
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:07,290
This way.

137
00:12:07,393 --> 00:12:10,294
And the women, Colonel.

138
00:12:10,396 --> 00:12:12,864
<i>My God, the women. </i>

139
00:12:12,965 --> 00:12:16,196
<i>Bare</i>-<i>breasted beauties</i>
<i>under trees... </i>

140
00:12:16,302 --> 00:12:18,964
