to wear that uniform?

160
00:13:27,039 --> 00:13:29,507
I'm entitled to do
anything I want.

161
00:13:29,608 --> 00:13:31,940
<i>[Passes Gas]</i>

162
00:13:32,044 --> 00:13:35,207
<i>Mr. Vanderbilt, I came down here</i>
<i>on your invitation. </i>

163
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:39,273
I did not come here to be insulted.
If you'll excuse me.

164
00:13:39,385 --> 00:13:40,875
Sit down!

165
00:13:40,986 --> 00:13:44,046
Please. Colonel, please.

166
00:13:44,156 --> 00:13:46,056
