167
00:13:47,193 --> 00:13:51,152
- Does Nicaragua mean anything to you, Walker?
- Nothing at all.

168
00:13:51,263 --> 00:13:55,461
Nicaragua's a fucked-up little country
somewhere south of here.

169
00:13:55,568 --> 00:13:59,299
<i>This worthless piece of real estate</i>
<i>controls the overland route to the Pacific. </i>

170
00:13:59,405 --> 00:14:01,566
