to go down there and take over.

178
00:14:22,061 --> 00:14:24,256
I want that country stable.

179
00:14:24,363 --> 00:14:26,661
I want it done now.

180
00:14:28,367 --> 00:14:31,666
They, uh... They tell me
you're a clever man, Walker.

181
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:34,500
Doctor, lawyer, surgeon.

182
00:14:34,607 --> 00:14:37,804
All that Renaissance rubbish
they talk about these days.

183
00:14:37,910 --> 00:14:39,878
<i>[Men Chattering In Chinese]</i>

184
00:14:53,826 --> 00:14:57,193
<i>Well? Can you handle thejob? </i>

185
00:15:01,734 --> 00:15:04,225
That's not the issue.

186
00:15:04,336 --> 00:15:06,304
