187
00:15:06,405 --> 00:15:08,373
<i>start a newspaper. </i>

188
00:15:09,642 --> 00:15:12,839
Then you would be wasting one
of life's golden moments, sir.

189
00:15:12,945 --> 00:15:17,075
It is not every man who is offered
the chance to have a country of his own.

190
00:15:18,984 --> 00:15:21,145
