191
00:15:23,188 --> 00:15:28,353
Walker's goals involve a higher purpose
than the vulgar pursuit of personal power.

192
00:15:29,595 --> 00:15:31,495
Huh.

193
00:15:32,932 --> 00:15:36,459
Do you prize democracy, Walker?

194
00:15:36,568 --> 00:15:38,468
Universal suffrage?

195
00:15:39,772 --> 00:15:42,263
The principles of our founding fathers?

196
00:15:43,709 --> 00:15:46,439
Yes.

197
00:15:46,545 --> 00:15:49,343
